rustsbtc trust compnay of south dakota was established in  to accommodate clients who wish to create south dakota trusts and take advantage of this states attractive laws our south dakota affiliate is a fullservice trust company which meets the full range of trust needsclick here to learn more private client servicesproviding for your family today helping preserve wealth for future generationswhether your goal is meeting the costs of a childs education or securing a comfortable retirement ― or both ― our wealth advisors can help you build your plan and offer taxefficient strategies for the acquisition growth preservation and distribution of your wealthlearn more btc capital managementregionally known and nationally ranked​btc capital is an affiliate of bankers trust and an sec registered investment advisor we provide portfolio management consulting and investment management services to institutional and highnetworth clients learn more custody and asset servicingsafeguard your assets with a custodian you can trustbankers trust is a leading provider of custodial services to retirement plans endowments and other institutional investors we understand the importance of exceptional custody and safekeeping of your assetsand investing in innovative solutions to better serve youand your clients  learn more thebankers trustdifferencestay safeat bankers trust there is no higher priority than the security of our customer’s assetslearn more about trusteer retirement plan services​​in todays competitive environment offering a quality retirement plan is critical to attracting and retaining a topperforming workforce bankers trust offers highquality customized retirement plans with sophisticated options — without burdening your organization with administrative tasksplan accessmeet the team btc trust company of south dakota​​see how south dakota trusts can benefit you note nondeposit investment services are not insured by fdic or any government agency and are not bank guaranteed they are not deposits and may lose value ​contact ussupportcustomer serviceaccount logins  site sections working with us individuals and families business and institutions financial partners about bankers trust access links contact us locations additional links careers ethicspoint bankers trust site btc capital management btcomplete south dakota trust services  bankers trust company all rights reserved equal opportunity employer wealthmanagementbankerstrust bankers trust turn on more accessible mode turn off more accessible mode it looks like your browser does not have javascript enabled please turn on javascript and try again resources contact us switch kit locations find an atm login to account business personal business internet banking remote deposit services retirement plan access addvantage weblink access ezcard ezbusiness credit card scorecard return check viewer lockbox iview portal lockbox iremit portal mypaycard employer access cash vault order access personal internet banking retirement plan access addvantage weblink access ezcard credit card scorecard gift card family cash card mypaycard employee access show sections personal commercial and business financial institutions wealth management about us more atms in more places​your bankers trust debit card provides access to  feefree atms look for these logos at any atm click here to find an atm near youforeign currency exchange​traveling overseas on business or just returning we can exchange us currency into other convertible currencies or the reverse when needed  if you have an account with usplease allow up to  days to process your ordervisit any of our branches to take advantage of this servicejoin our centennial celebrationbankers trust first opened its doors on june  you’re invited to help us celebrate our th anniversary by attending a centennial event at a bankers trust location near you click here to find an event near you personal bankingwe are dedicated to achieving your personal financial needs  from 