hecking reservehome equity advances bankers trust company was formerly known as bankers trust company national association and changed its name to bankers trust company in december  the company was founded in  and is based in des moines iowa with branches in the greater des moines metro and ames iowa it has operations in phoenix arizona omaha nebraska and sioux falls south dakota it has a charter bank in cedar rapids iowa bankers trust company operates as a subsidiary of midamerica financial corporation detailed description  th streetdes moines ia united statesfounded in  phone  fax  key executives for bankers trust company mr suku v radia chief executive officer and director age  mr donald j coffin president mr kip albertson chief financial officer mr tim kintner executive vice president of regional banking markets and community relations mr scott d eltjes senior vice president of investment management and wealth management age  compensation as of fiscal year  bankers trust company key developments bankers trust co promotes don coffin to president effective march   feb   don coffin who joined bankers trust co in  as senior vice president of lending has been promoted to president effective march   in  coffin was promoted to executive vice president and chief lending officer and currently manages a team of lenders with a loan portfolio exceeding  billion before joining bankers trust coffin served as the managing director of national commercial banking with the privatebank and trust co he also held the position of senior vice president and central region leader at lasalle national bank where he managed the colorado nebraska and iowa offices similar private companies by industry company name region  bancorp united states  bancorp mhc united states st financial bank usa united states st manatee bank united states st national bank united states recent private companies transactions typedate target bankruptcy november   bcdg lp request profile update   the information and